Yeah, Minime, Dark One asked for reinforcements.

::Striker::

Striker growls, two shots hitting him in the chest. He looks back at Savage, 
continuing to fire on the bot.

Striker holds his fire as he sees Tamtron unite, his eyes widening as he sees 
him fire his weapon at Spears. Acting quickly, Striker aims his missile 
launcher, firing a missile in the path of the shot, hoping it'd at least 
deflect it.
